sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS Reencrypt
    participant RBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS<br/>SubjectAccessReview
    participant API as DS Pipeline API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant DB as MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP MySQL
    participant S3 as S3 Object Storage<br/>9000/443 HTTP/HTTPS
    participant WFC as Argo Workflow Controller
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Pods as Pipeline Step Pods
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant PA as Persistence Agent

    Note over User, PA: Flow 1: Pipeline Submission and Execution

    User->>Route: POST /apis/v2beta1/pipelines<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Route->>RBAC: Forward (TLS Reencrypt)
    RBAC->>RBAC: SubjectAccessReview<br/>(DSPA api subresource)
    RBAC->>API: Proxied request<br/>TLS (service-ca)
    API->>DB: Store pipeline metadata<br/>TLS (when PodToPodTLS)<br/>Auth: DB password
    API->>S3: Store pipeline artifacts<br/>TLS (configurable)<br/>Auth: AccessKey/SecretKey
    API-->>RBAC: Pipeline created
    RBAC-->>Route: Response
    Route-->>User: JSON Response

    Note over User, PA: Pipeline Execution

    User->>Route: POST /apis/v2beta1/runs
    Route->>RBAC: Forward
    RBAC->>API: Create run
    API->>DB: Store run record
    API-->>User: Run created

    WFC->>K8s: Watch Workflow CRs<br/>TLS, ServiceAccount token
    K8s-->>WFC: New Workflow event
    WFC->>K8s: Create step pods
    K8s-->>Pods: Schedule pods

    Pods->>MLMD: Report execution metadata<br/>gRPC/8080, TLS (PodToPodTLS)<br/>NetworkPolicy controlled
    Pods->>API: Report step status<br/>8888/TCP, TLS (PodToPodTLS)
    PA->>API: Sync workflow status<br/>8888/TCP, TLS (PodToPodTLS)

    Note over User, PA: Flow 2: MLMD Metadata Access (External)

    participant MRoute as OpenShift Route<br/>(MLMD) 443/TCP
    participant MRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>(MLMD) 8443/TCP
    participant Envoy as MLMD Envoy Proxy<br/>9090/TCP HTTP

    User->>MRoute: GET metadata<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    MRoute->>MRBAC: Forward (TLS Reencrypt)
    MRBAC->>MRBAC: SubjectAccessReview
    MRBAC->>Envoy: Proxied (HTTP/9090)
    Envoy->>MLMD: gRPC/8080<br/>TLS (PodToPodTLS)
    MLMD->>DB: Query lineage data<br/>MySQL/3306, TLS
    DB-->>MLMD: Results
    MLMD-->>Envoy: gRPC response
    Envoy-->>MRBAC: HTTP response
    MRBAC-->>MRoute: HTTPS
    MRoute-->>User: Metadata response

    Note over User, PA: Flow 3: Managed Pipelines Validation

    participant DSPO as DSPO Controller
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    DSPO->>OCI: Fetch managed-pipelines.json<br/>HTTPS/443, Keychain auth
    OCI-->>DSPO: Manifest (cached 10min TTL)
    DSPO->>DSPO: Validate CR pipeline names<br/>against manifest
    DSPO->>API: Deploy with validated<br/>managed pipelines config
